==Spanish==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[tenere|tenēre]]

=== Pronunciation ===
*[[IPA]]: /tener/
*[[SAMPA]]: /tener/

=== Transitive verb ===
[[Category:Spanish verbs]]
'''tener'''

# to [[have]]
#: ''Tengo seis hermanos.'' - "I have six brothers."
# to [[hold]]
#: ''Ten esto.'' - "Hold this."
# to [[feel]]; to [[make]] 
#: ''Tengo frío.'' - "I am cold."
#: ''Eso nos tiene lastimos.'' - "That makes us sad."
'''tener por'''
# to [[think]]; to be of the [[opinion]]
#: ''Te tengo por loco.'' - "I think you are crazy."
'''tener que'''
# to have to
#: ''Tengo que salir ahora.'' - "I have to leave now."

